      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'You are a monster alien parasite just escaped from Area 51, ready to consume
    anything and everything in site to grow and destroy everything or will you be
    stopped?

    Eat as much as you can to grow while watching out for flying hazards
    they will shoot at you and ground obstacles that can launch you to your death.
    You will die if your lives or size reaches 0.

    The bar at the top middle
    of your srceen is your size meter. You start at a size of 5 and  must have a
    large enough size to eat certain objects.


    Use RIGHT/LEFT arrow keys to
    move forward/backwards.

    Use the UP arrow key to jump and DOWN arrow key
    to dive.

    Press SPACE key to shoot projectiles to destroy certain hazards.


    Power
    Ups:

    Blue - Plus one life

    Green - Jump boost for 15 seconds

    Red
    - Ability to break ground hazards for 15 seconds'
